---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer>
  <div class="container footer-inner">
    <p>
      Emissions modelled with the <a href="https://www.thegreenwebfoundation.org/co2-js/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sustainable Web Design model (CO2.js)</a>.
      Hosting checked against the <a href="https://www.thegreenwebfoundation.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Green Web Foundation</a> registry.
    </p>
    <p>&copy; {year} Green Orbit Digital. Reports regenerate automatically.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--goa-navy-line);
    padding: 28px 0 40px;
    margin-top: 60px;
    color: var(--goa-text-dim);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .footer-inner p { margin: 0 0 6px; }
</style>
